profile_summary: As a seasoned web2 and web3 developer with a strong background in TypeScript, Python, and JavaScript, I leverage my expertise to build innovative solutions, with a focus on blockchain technology and a proven track record of participating in over 5 hackathons. With a network of 103 followers and 123 public repositories, I'm committed to delivering high-quality developments and collaborations. I'm excited to connect and explore opportunities, and can be reached at amanzishan.az@gmail.com or through my social media profiles on Twitter and LinkedIn.
